  • class KnownDim (n :: k) where
    • data Dim (x :: k) :: forall k. k -> * where
      • pattern D :: forall (n :: Nat). () => KnownDim n => Dim n
      • pattern Dim :: forall k (n :: k). () => KnownDim n => Dim n
      • pattern Dn :: forall (xn :: XNat). KnownXNatType xn => forall (n :: Nat). (KnownDim n, xn ~ N n) => Dim n -> Dim xn
      • pattern Dx :: forall (xn :: XNat). KnownXNatType xn => forall (n :: Nat) (m :: Nat). (KnownDim n, MinDim m n, xn ~ XN m) => Dim n -> Dim xn
    • class Dimensions (ds :: [k]) where
      • type family All (f :: k -> Constraint) (xs :: [k]) :: Constraint where ...
      • type Dims (xs :: [k]) = TypedList (Dim :: k -> *) xs
      • data SomeDims where
        • SomeDims :: SomeDims
      • newtype Idx (n :: k) :: forall k. k -> * = Idx {
        • unIdx :: Word
        }
      • compareDim :: Dim a -> Dim b -> Ordering
      • compareDim' :: (KnownDim a, KnownDim b) => p a -> q b -> Ordering
      • constrain :: KnownDim m => Dim x -> Maybe (Dim (XN m))
      • constrainBy :: Dim m -> Dim x -> Maybe (Dim (XN m))
      • dimVal :: Dim x -> Word
      • dimVal' :: KnownDim n => Word
      • inferDimLE :: MinDim m n => Evidence (m <= n)
      • minusDim :: MinDim m n => Dim n -> Dim m -> Dim (n - m)
      • minusDimM :: Dim n -> Dim m -> Maybe (Dim (n - m))
      • plusDim :: Dim n -> Dim m -> Dim (n + m)
      • powerDim :: Dim n -> Dim m -> Dim (n ^ m)
      • relax :: MinDim m n => Dim (XN n) -> Dim (XN m)
      • sameDim :: Dim x -> Dim y -> Maybe (Evidence (x ~ y))
      • sameDim' :: (KnownDim x, KnownDim y) => p x -> q y -> Maybe (Evidence (x ~ y))
      • someDimVal :: Word -> SomeDim
      • timesDim :: Dim n -> Dim m -> Dim (n * m)
      • asSpaceOf :: a ds -> (b ds -> c) -> b ds -> c
      • compareDims :: Dims as -> Dims bs -> Ordering
      • compareDims' :: (Dimensions as, Dimensions bs) => p as -> q bs -> Ordering
      • inSpaceOf :: a ds -> b ds -> a ds
